hive.org/web/20151009234755/http://www.teluguaspirant.com/india-us-relations/207/ Highlights of Indo-U.S Visit 2015]\n* [http://news.biharprabha.com/2013/09/highlights-of-india-us-bilateral-ties-and-cooperation-as-of-2013/ Highlights of India US Bilateral Ties and Cooperation as of 2013]\n* Blake, Jr., Robert O. \"U.S.-India Relations: the Making of a Comprehensive Relationship.\" U.S. official speech at India's Army War College, August 23, 2004; [https://web.archive.org/web/20130305081436/http://merln.ndu.edu/archivepdf/india/State/35686.pdf online]\n* [https://history.state.gov/countries/india History of India \u2013 U.S. Relations], official U.S. site\n* [https://opencrs.com/document/RL33529/ India-U.S. Relations] [[Congressional Research Service]]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20061202152247/http://www.indianembassy.org/newsite/induspolAug06.asp Indian Embassy: India \u2013 U.S. Relations: A General Overview], official Indian site\n* [http://www.nbr.org/research/activity.aspx?id=176 Deepening U.S.-India Economic Engagement], Q&A with U.S. Ambassador Susan Esserman (September 2011)\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110721015037/http://www.nbr.org/research/activity.aspx?id=155 A Way Forward in U.S.-India Defense Cooperation], July 2011 interview with [[Stephen P. Cohen]] and Sunil Dasgupta\n* [http://www.nbr.org/research/activity.aspx?id=146 Charting the Future of U.S.-India Relations], June 2011 interview with Ambassador [[Thomas R. Pickering]]\n* [https://2001-2009.state.gov/p/sca/rls/rm/22615.htm U.S. Department of state: The Future of US-India Relations]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20120623140500/http://www.fas.usda.gov/itp/us-india.asp U.S. Department of Agriculture: U.S.\u2013India Trade Relations]\n\n{{Foreign relations of India}}\n{{Foreign relations of the United States}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:India-United States relations}}\n[[Category:India\u2013United States relations| ]]\n[[Category:Bilateral relations of the United States]]\n[[Category:Bilateral rel